
@startuml
' Team Sports Scouting System - Class Diagram

class Employee {
  +id: int
  +name: String
  +role: String
}

class HeadCoach << (C, #FFBBBB) >> {
  +identifyPlayerProfiles(): PlayerProfile
  +reviewScoutingReports(): void
  +selectPlayersForShortList(): void
}

class Director << (C, #BBFFBB) >> {
  +makeOfficialOffer(Player): void
}

class Scout << (C, #BBFFFF) >> {
  +notePlayerOnLongList(Player): void
  +submitScoutingReport(Player): ScoutingReport
}

class Player {
  +id: int
  +name: String
  +position: String
  +attributes: Map<String, Integer>
}

class PlayerProfile {
  +targetPosition: String
  +attributes: Map<String, Integer>
}

class ScoutingReport {
  +player: Player
  +pros: List<String>
  +cons: List<String>
  +recommendation: String
}

class LongList {
  +players: List<Player>
}

class ShortList {
  +players: List<Player>
}

class ScoutingAssignment {
  +player: Player
  +scout: Scout
  +status: String
  +report: ScoutingReport
}

' Relationships

Employee <|-- HeadCoach
Employee <|-- Director
Employee <|-- Scout

HeadCoach "1" --> "0..*" PlayerProfile
HeadCoach "1" --> "0..*" ShortList
HeadCoach "1" --> "0..*" ScoutingReport

Director "1" --> "0..*" Player

Scout "1" --> "0..*" LongList
Scout "1" --> "0..*" ScoutingAssignment
Scout "1" --> "0..*" ScoutingReport

PlayerProfile "1" --> "0..*" Player

LongList "1" --> "0..*" Player
ShortList "1" --> "0..*" Player

ScoutingAssignment "1" --> "1" ScoutingReport
ScoutingAssignment "1" --> "1" Player
ScoutingAssignment "1" --> "1" Scout

@enduml

### Explanation of Key Elements:
- **Employee**: Base class for all club personnel.
- **HeadCoach**, **Director**, and **Scout**: Subclasses of `Employee` with specific roles.
- **Player**: Represents players being scouted.
- **PlayerProfile**: Defines target profiles that the head coach sets.
- **ScoutingReport**: Contains evaluation details from scouts.
- **LongList** and **ShortList**: Lists of players under consideration.
- **ScoutingAssignment**: Represents a task assigned to a scout to investigate a player.

